texts.html: May 31, 2015May 31, 2015 | TJScotson

Hello internet, and welcome to my new home in the cloud! Hopefully a dramatic upgrade from my old messy blogroll of work, this site will serves as my hub of everything I do as a creator. Certain examples of my short fiction, extracts from larger works, and several of my poems can be found here as well as contact information and directions to where you can buy all of my various publications.
text: Hello internet, and welcome to my new home in the cloud! Hopefully a dramatic upgrade from my old messy blogroll of work, this site will serves as my hub of everything I do as a creator. Certain examples of my short fiction, extracts from larger works, and several of my poems can be found here as well as contact information and directions to where you can buy all of my various publications.

texts.html: The blog element that you are reading here is where I will be keeping all you fine people up to date with what I’m doing, where you can catch me and whatever happens to be on my mind. It’s also where I’ll post articles and extended thoughts on things such as the various event reviews you’ve seen recently, or short essays on topic I’ve been thinking about. Several of these have been migrated over from my previous site and can be found in the archives here. There will hopefully be much more to come!
